        "min": 10,
        "max": 5000,
        "unit": "mm/s",
        "value": 1500,
        "description": "Effective for contaminant removal without excessive heat buildup; recommended 1500 mm/s for optimal balance on Poplar. Slower (500-1000 mm/s) for heavy contamination, faster (2000-3000 mm/s) for light. From industry standards in Laser Cleaning Handbook (SPI Lasers, 2020)."
      },
