        "min": 1,
        "max": 10,
        "unit": "passes",
        "value": 2,
        "description": "Single pass for light contamination, multi-pass for heavy; 2 passes recommended for complete removal on Poplar without damage. Industry practice from case studies in J. Clean. Prod. (2020)."
